flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Launch Streamlit App]
    B --> C[DatabaseManager creates SQLite table]
    C --> D[BrowserHistory loads data from DB]
    D --> E[Reconstruct Doubly Linked List]
    E --> F{User Action}
    F -->|Visit URL| G[Create new Node]
    G --> H[Set prev = current node]
    H --> I[Set current.next = new node]
    I --> J[Delete forward history nodes]
    J --> K[Merge node into list]
    K --> L[Save to SQLite]
    L --> F
    F -->|Back| M[Move current = current.prev]
    M --> N[Update DB is_current flag]
    N --> F
    F -->|Forward| O[Move current = current.next]
    O --> P[Update DB is_current flag]
    P --> F
    F -->|Search| Q[Traverse list & match URL]
    Q --> R[Display matching results]
    R --> F
    F -->|Delete| S[Remove node from list]
    S --> T[Fix prev/next pointers]
    T --> U[Save to SQLite]
    U --> F
    F -->|Clear History| V[Remove all nodes]
    V --> W[Delete all SQLite records]
    W --> F
    F -->|Exit| X([End])
